WEBVTT

00:04.078 --> 00:08.289
_

00:08.578 --> 00:12.305
<font color="#fff00">Synced
by Bakugan</font>

00:15.558 --> 00:19.311
AARON MAHNKE: On a cold night
in the late fifth century,

00:19.353 --> 00:20.938
a man named Patricius

00:20.980 --> 00:23.357
walked down a lonely road in Ireland.

00:27.445 --> 00:29.488
Patricius was on a mission...

00:30.865 --> 00:32.533
to spread the Gospel.

00:36.328 --> 00:39.832
But the road he walked was never easy.

00:44.503 --> 00:46.380
Fifth Century pagans

00:46.422 --> 00:49.842
weren't always receptive
to the teachings of Christ,

00:49.884 --> 00:52.344
especially in the village of Ossory.

00:54.346 --> 00:56.098
- [ANIMAL GROWLING]
- [CHAINS CLANKING]

00:56.140 --> 00:57.850
That's because

00:57.892 --> 01:01.312
the people of Ossory already had a god.

01:03.439 --> 01:05.649
They worshiped the wolf.

01:08.277 --> 01:09.445
[GASP]

01:14.492 --> 01:16.035
PATRICIUS: I come

01:16.076 --> 01:19.330
in the name of Jesus Christ.

01:19.371 --> 01:21.415
[HOWLING]

01:21.457 --> 01:23.501
Patricius' message held no power

01:23.542 --> 01:25.252
for the people of Ossory.

01:27.046 --> 01:30.132
And their leader had no
use for his salvation.

01:30.174 --> 01:32.718
[ROARING]

01:34.929 --> 01:36.597
[GRUNTING]

01:38.933 --> 01:42.520
It seemed like the end
of the road for Patricius.

01:44.480 --> 01:46.065
And then...

01:46.106 --> 01:48.025
[SHOUTING]

01:48.067 --> 01:50.402
something strange began to happen

01:50.444 --> 01:52.071
to one of the villagers...

01:52.112 --> 01:53.906
[GROWLING]

01:53.948 --> 01:58.494
...an ungodly transformation
from man to beast.

01:58.536 --> 02:00.454
[SNARLING]

02:02.414 --> 02:04.208
Villager by villager,

02:04.250 --> 02:07.002
this unnatural
metamorphosis continued...

02:08.545 --> 02:11.340
until they became a savage pack.

02:16.053 --> 02:18.347
But it wasn't Patricius they wanted.

02:20.000 --> 02:26.074
